Qualys ssl checker
https://www.ssllabs.com/ssltest/?_ga=1.68563409.1998881531.1429745802

asafaweb <- asp.net and others
http://www.google.com/transparencyreport/saferemail/

cookie invalidation is essential to security.

username enumeration... how big of a problem is this?

don't leak information in the url or error messages.

Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate, max-age=0; <- for sensitive information make sure this is handled.

watch out for userids in the url and make sure that the stuff is locked down appropriately.

